snippet.title: Monster Hunter Online - Expansion 2.0 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Teaser Trailer for Expansion 2.0 of Monster Hunter Online!

New monsters like;
Gravios
Flame Blangonga
Lavasioth
Rajang
And new forms of Merphistophelin!
